<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Headlong1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Headlong,</orth> adv. with the head foremost: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.149" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 149</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 24</bibl>. Hence == without ceremony: <cit><quote>hence will I drag thee h. by the heels,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.86" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 10, 86</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>